  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates the COU at Model Risk Level 3 following an expansion of the intended use to include off-label paediatric flow regimes. Thirteen credibility factors are addressed; twelve are fully assessed and one (Equivalency of input parameters) is treated as not requiring assessment on the grounds that the validation dataset geometry is nominally identical to the device geometry—an argument that conflates geometric equivalency with full input-parameter equivalency and therefore does not satisfy the factorStatus 'not-applicable' threshold.",
