    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. The equivalency of input parameters factor was not formally assessed on the basis that the validation geometry is nominally identical to the device geometry; the team judged this sufficient for the adult CPB operating envelope. The overall credibility evidence is considered adequate to support the submission decision for the primary adult CPB indication. The paediatric extension is noted as a residual uncertainty.",
